data.name: Label12.Text
data.value:
This is your last chance to go back if you would like to change these settings, or to abort the transformation.
Once started, the transformation process cannot be cancelled until it is complete. If you're sure you want to begin the transformation, click Transform.

data.name: Label26.Text
data.value: If you are sure you don't want to ever go back to how this computer looked before the transformation, choose this option to permanently delete the backups made of system files during transformation and uninstall this program.
